Day 45 – Road to Fluent Spanish Summary
Today focused on continued reinforcement of travel-oriented conversational Spanish while advancing deeper into conversational grammar and present perfect structures through Pimsleur Unit 1 review. Duolingo review introduced new vocabulary and descriptive conversational phrases including “limpio,” “dieta saludable,” “reloj,” “barrio,” and clothing/accessory-related vocabulary such as “pulsera” and “aretes.” Memrise review reinforced ownership structures and descriptive conversational phrases, including:

Esta pluma es mía
Esos aretes
Creo que esta pulsera es de mi madre
